IMAPStore proton-remote
  Host 127.0.0.1
  Port 1143
  User chris@chrisderose.com
  PassCmd "/usr/bin/gpg2 -q --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d ~/.mbsyncpass.gpg"
  TLSType STARTTLS
  CertificateFile ~/.config/protonmail/bridge-v3/cert.pem

MaildirStore proton-local
  SubFolders Verbatim
  Path ~/.local/share/mbsync/
  Inbox ~/.local/share/mbsync/Inbox

Channel proton
  Far :proton-remote:
  Near :proton-local:
  Patterns * !Labels* !"All Mail"
  Create Both
  Expunge Both
  SyncState *
